      • createIngestContracts

        RequestResponse createIngestContracts(VitamContext vitamContext,
                                      InputStream ingestContracts)
                               throws InvalidParseOperationException,
                                      AccessExternalClientException
        create a set of ingest contracts after passing the validation steps. If all the contracts are valid, they are stored in the collection and indexed.
        The input is invalid in the following situations :
        • The json is invalid
        • The json contains 2 ore many contracts having the same name
        • One or more mandatory field is missing
        • A field has an invalid format
        • One or many contracts elready exist in the database
        Parameters:
        vitamContext - the vitam context
        ingestContracts - as InputStream
        Returns:
        Vitam response
        Throws:
        InvalidParseOperationException
        AccessExternalClientException
